{"tid":1726953,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[木馬屠城記] 老解=中共體制既一部分, 唔該唔好再玩膠吹奏, 隨時會蝴蝶效應","createTime":"2019-11-16T09:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T13:17:18.000Z","uid":56729,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3e74051c3e291d0942827f7d912ea89a4ffb3cdd","tid":1726953,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:51:00.000Z","msg":"屌哂班玩膠吹奏撚三毛<br />\n今日出黎班老解隨時有份殺過D浮屍<br />\n宜家仲吹奏佢地<br />\n點對得住之前犧牲左既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對家今次既做法好明顯就係引發破窗效應<br />\n製做一個老解都有好人既假象<br />\n所謂贏得民心之後就做乜都得<br />\n仲兒戲過木馬屠城記<br />\n我地玩膠吹奏<br />\n變相就係幫左中共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家要做既<br />\n就係加強文宣<br />\n宣傳出老解帶黎既壞處同恐慌<br />\n防止風向吹到有利對家<br />\n所以拜託唔好再玩膠<br />\n今次真係可以玩出事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75adea3353a332c0099ce01b960c2278ab1cbf2e","tid":1726953,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:21:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2326e6da753abffa0aeda95ab760f9f25164ce7","tid":1726953,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:24:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2ea5a25b36c1c7ad2a3420e22d8a73f8c396b1df","tid":1726953,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:17:18.000Z","msg":"其實出解放軍係國際核彈嘅另一論調<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1727524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1727524</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}